ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectNo. 142 - (Quebec) Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER N° 142 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the federal government to provide financial assistance to the province of QUEBEC with respect to the STORM that affected the areas of Bas-St-Laurent, Capitale-Nationale, Côte-Nord and Gaspésie from December 5 to December 7, 2010.
